epi-PMD.def: We measure PM2.5 exposure using the number of age-standardized disability-adjusted life-years lost per 100,000 persons (DALY rate) due to exposure to fine air particulate matter smaller than 2.5 micrometers (PM2.5).
epi-PMD.name: Ambient particulate matter pollution
epi-PMD.source: Institute for Health Metrics and Evaluation
